{"tid":735742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好黑仔呀 搬遷先比人順手牽羊","createTime":"2018-07-09T17:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T17:17:34.000Z","uid":173785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5c845916ab226baf94507d8be6393eac00256d","tid":735742,"uid":173785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"今日搬舖嘅時候貨車裝唔落張櫈，要等下一轉車，跟住就比人拎左，張櫈有轆，輕鬆拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上圖片 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/010148_d33a87a8a11b0c9d787c3bb354da11e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F010148_d33a87a8a11b0c9d787c3bb354da11e6.png&h=dfd58d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/010149_f7e3206984876de4a9ec0106364c8f55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F010149_f7e3206984876de4a9ec0106364c8f55.png&h=d9a25c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地拎走哂啲攬枕得返架木櫈諗住下一轉車再上，結果返到黎嘅時候已經比人抬走左。問左保安話走左幾分鐘，我追出去都已經見唔到人影。保安話cctv影到佢地其中一位係正門入，另一位就係有入到lift，兩位都影到哂正面，見佢地係後門出(要行一層樓梯，張野都幾重下)，約7點45-8點左右拎走左，叫我地聽日再睇返閉錄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發生地點係觀塘時運工業大廈。頭先暫時睇到保安手機影到背面係著白T + 牛仔。<br />\n<br />\n因為張櫈連運費都買左三千幾蚊，只求盡快搵返，大家都唔想搞咁多野，希望拎左嘅人盡快聯絡返我地歸還木櫈，必不追究！<br />\n<br />\nbtw 有無巴絲今日係觀塘有見到有2個男人推住呢隻木櫈，入左邊一幢大廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n借朋友ac一post<br />\n請聯絡我: iy.ytshan@gmail.com"},{"pid":"d41cc1335b8a4d8dd468d3b8867087f36d5243ab","tid":735742,"uid":42379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"做咩開新post"},{"pid":"de99be9a21bb43f28f9e96a656a43e4d81e59de3","tid":735742,"uid":173785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"Partner 叫我改標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}